WEBVTT

00:09:59.167 --> 00:10:02.893
Men talk always, women just sitting there,

00:10:02.917 --> 00:10:04.184
but in the back.

00:10:04.208 --> 00:10:06.143
They are not there to take any decision.

00:10:06.167 --> 00:10:09.893
So after the men figure out
all the knowledge,

00:10:09.917 --> 00:10:13.226
we say, well, you call the women,
"Come and have a look."

00:10:13.250 --> 00:10:14.559
They say, "Yes, sure,"

00:10:14.583 --> 00:10:16.681
because they've already done 
the first work.

00:10:16.685 --> 00:10:17.976
(Laughter)

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:19.768
When the women come,

00:10:19.792 --> 00:10:22.518
and they look at the map,
they're like, "Mm, no."

00:10:22.542 --> 00:10:24.018
(Laughter)

00:10:24.042 --> 00:10:25.309
"This is wrong.

00:10:25.333 --> 00:10:28.601
Here's where I collect the medicine.
Here's where I collect the food.

00:10:28.625 --> 00:10:30.226
Here's where I collect --"